1
00:00:05,724 --> 00:00:08,420
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,493 --> 00:00:12,361
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,431 --> 00:00:16,424
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,768 --> 00:00:19,259
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,338 --> 00:00:23,399
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,475 --> 00:00:27,434
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,914 --> 00:00:33,647
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,353 --> 00:00:37,322
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,758 --> 00:00:41,851
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,594 --> 00:00:43,891
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,229 --> 00:00:46,789
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,840 --> 00:01:00,210
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,412 --> 00:01:01,572
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,647 --> 00:01:05,447
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,784 --> 00:01:10,983
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,256 --> 00:01:12,587
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,658 --> 00:01:14,057
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,126 --> 00:01:20,395
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:38,161 --> 00:01:43,497
<i>Akamaru Trembles.</i>
<i>Gaara's Cruel Strength!</i>

20
00:01:55,945 --> 00:01:56,912
<i>That guy...?</i>

21
00:01:57,547 --> 00:01:58,571
Everyone hide!

22
00:01:58,648 --> 00:02:00,343
No, lie low quick!

23
00:02:01,050 --> 00:02:02,847
W-Where is that guy?

24
00:02:04,353 --> 00:02:05,342
Naruto...

25
00:02:06,122 --> 00:02:09,853
<i>That fool, he finally woke up.</i>

26
00:02:14,063 --> 00:02:16,497
You are quite one of a kind.

27
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:19,694
Actually, you are getting on my nerves.

28
00:02:27,643 --> 00:02:29,008
Sakura!

29
00:02:29,545 --> 00:02:31,809
- What?
- Y-Y-Your!

30
00:02:32,148 --> 00:02:34,480
Sakura... your hair!

31
00:02:34,684 --> 00:02:36,879
Oh! This?

32
00:02:39,021 --> 00:02:42,115
I'm changing my image,
changing my image!

33
00:02:45,428 --> 00:02:48,022
I like it better long but,

34
00:02:48,331 --> 00:02:50,799
when I move around in
a forest like this,

35
00:02:50,867 --> 00:02:52,562
it gets in the way if it's long.

36
00:02:55,605 --> 00:02:56,799
By the way...

37
00:02:57,073 --> 00:03:00,406
why are you guys here?!

38
00:03:00,777 --> 00:03:05,111
Hah... It's such a pain
to explain it to you.

39
00:03:05,782 --> 00:03:07,875
Everybody helped out.

40
00:03:08,217 --> 00:03:08,876
Huh?

41
00:03:10,820 --> 00:03:12,879
<i>Sakura's putting on a show of bravado...</i>

42
00:03:15,992 --> 00:03:17,687
I'll take care of him from here.

43
00:03:18,294 --> 00:03:20,228
Ah... Okay...

44
00:03:20,763 --> 00:03:23,357
Keep it together! Lee!

45
00:03:27,203 --> 00:03:30,900
Oh? Tenten, why are you here?

46
00:03:31,107 --> 00:03:32,438
I came to help.

47
00:03:33,309 --> 00:03:34,139
Huh?

48
00:03:34,744 --> 00:03:36,644
Those guys,
where's the Sound Village Ninjas?

49
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:39,309
A kid named Sasuke
drove them away!

50
00:03:40,817 --> 00:03:41,784
Really...

51
00:03:42,885 --> 00:03:45,547
Why did you hastily decide
to act on your own?!

52
00:03:46,088 --> 00:03:47,646
Besides, you really got beaten up!

53
00:03:48,958 --> 00:03:53,292
S-Sakura was in danger.
So as a man, I...

54
00:03:54,397 --> 00:03:55,455
<i>You're kidding!</i>

55
00:03:55,698 --> 00:03:58,963
<i>If it were Lee alone,</i>
<i>he wouldn't have lost to those guys.</i>

56
00:03:59,769 --> 00:04:01,760
You're really stupid.

57
00:04:03,973 --> 00:04:06,168
I can't argue with that.

58
00:04:06,576 --> 00:04:09,568
You, Bushy Brow!

59
00:04:10,079 --> 00:04:11,171
Naruto!

60
00:04:11,347 --> 00:04:15,010
Don't say rude things to Lee!

61
00:04:17,486 --> 00:04:18,578
<i>What in the world...</i>

62
00:04:18,654 --> 00:04:21,418
<i>happened while I was asleep?</i>

63
00:04:23,125 --> 00:04:26,390
That Naruto,
he's completely out of the loop.

64
00:04:26,863 --> 00:04:31,061
He's not the type to be
the protagonist of a story, certainly not.

65
00:04:34,804 --> 00:04:35,668
Lee...

66
00:04:37,073 --> 00:04:37,903
Thank you.

67
00:04:39,642 --> 00:04:42,805
Because of you,
I was able to wake up.

68
00:04:43,613 --> 00:04:45,843
I feel like I've gotten a little stronger!

69
00:04:50,586 --> 00:04:51,678
Sakura...

70
00:04:52,855 --> 00:04:57,224
It looks like my efforts
weren't enough!

71
00:04:58,227 --> 00:05:02,687
Sasuke... Just what you'd expect
from the Uchiha clan.

72
00:05:03,199 --> 00:05:04,996
To chase off the Sound Village Ninjas,

73
00:05:05,134 --> 00:05:08,331
just as I thought,
you possess amazing strength.

74
00:05:08,905 --> 00:05:10,964
I was beaten to a pulp.

75
00:05:11,207 --> 00:05:14,699
<i>What?! He was beaten to a pulp?!</i>

76
00:05:15,745 --> 00:05:17,235
What's he talking about?

77
00:05:17,513 --> 00:05:20,073
<i>Were those guys really that strong?</i>

78
00:05:21,384 --> 00:05:22,214
Sakura!

79
00:05:23,152 --> 00:05:25,484
The Lotus of Leaf Village
blooms twice.

80
00:05:25,588 --> 00:05:26,247
Huh?

81
00:05:27,023 --> 00:05:30,720
When we meet again,
I will have become a stronger man.

82
00:05:31,994 --> 00:05:32,892
I pledge it.

83
00:05:35,731 --> 00:05:36,493
Okay.

84
00:05:39,268 --> 00:05:40,428
Hey Sakura!

85
00:05:41,003 --> 00:05:42,231
Come here, come here!

86
00:05:42,638 --> 00:05:44,902
Your hair! I'll fix it for you!

87
00:05:46,842 --> 00:05:48,002
That'd be great.

88
00:05:54,150 --> 00:05:56,209
You are really sneaky.

89
00:05:56,385 --> 00:05:59,218
Hugging him like that,
you little billboard brow.

90
00:05:59,322 --> 00:06:03,656
It's called first come first served,
Miss Ino pig.

91
00:06:09,999 --> 00:06:12,559
<i>Sasuke... Uchiha.</i>

92
00:06:17,506 --> 00:06:20,373
<i>At any rate... he's a strong opponent.</i>

93
00:06:23,646 --> 00:06:25,307
Are you okay, Akamaru?

94
00:06:28,117 --> 00:06:29,379
Is he still shaking?

95
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:32,048
It's already been half a day.

96
00:06:33,389 --> 00:06:34,287
Akamaru...

97
00:06:35,191 --> 00:06:39,093
I don't blame him,
it's because he saw that thing...

98
00:06:43,065 --> 00:06:45,260
After all, brains are most important
in survival!

99
00:06:45,334 --> 00:06:47,029
Right. Akamaru?

100
00:06:48,771 --> 00:06:50,466
Lucky for us,

101
00:06:50,539 --> 00:06:53,133
the guys who got caught in
the trap had an earth scroll!

102
00:06:53,242 --> 00:06:56,234
We'll be the first to
the tower at this rate!

103
00:06:56,779 --> 00:07:00,306
Don't get carried away.
That's dangerous.

104
00:07:01,150 --> 00:07:04,950
No matter how small a bug it is,
it has to guard itself at all times.

105
00:07:05,621 --> 00:07:07,987
We have to pay attention to avoid
coming across any enemies...

106
00:07:09,058 --> 00:07:10,082
This is safety.

107
00:07:10,326 --> 00:07:12,123
I know that!

108
00:07:12,194 --> 00:07:16,426
As always, you're speaking in a way
that's difficult to understand, bug-nerd.

109
00:07:17,633 --> 00:07:21,364
Um... B-But...
What Shino said...

110
00:07:21,437 --> 00:07:22,870
He has a point.

111
00:07:23,339 --> 00:07:25,398
I know! C'mon.

112
00:07:26,675 --> 00:07:27,801
<i>Naruto...</i>

113
00:07:28,244 --> 00:07:29,677
<i>I hope nothing's happened to him...</i>

114
00:07:32,481 --> 00:07:33,880
Hey you two, stop.

115
00:07:36,352 --> 00:07:39,446
We're being careful not to
come across enemy, right?

116
00:07:40,056 --> 00:07:41,387
Then Hinata!

117
00:07:42,058 --> 00:07:44,822
Can you see 1 kilometer
in that direction?

118
00:07:46,262 --> 00:07:48,822
Yep... I'll have a look.
Byakugan!

119
00:07:55,638 --> 00:07:57,230
T-There's someone there.

120
00:08:00,810 --> 00:08:04,177
Evidently there are... 6 people...

121
00:08:04,613 --> 00:08:06,808
Okay! Let's go look!

122
00:08:07,116 --> 00:08:07,912
Huh?

123
00:08:08,284 --> 00:08:11,947
Kiba! What are you saying?
We're not doing that.

124
00:08:12,254 --> 00:08:14,154
The Proctor told us to bring

125
00:08:14,223 --> 00:08:16,691
one of each "Heaven" and "Earth"
scroll in a pair.

126
00:08:17,326 --> 00:08:19,886
He didn't say not to
take more than that.

127
00:08:20,563 --> 00:08:26,763
If we take more, that means
some other teams will be left out.

128
00:08:27,403 --> 00:08:28,802
B-But...

129
00:08:29,105 --> 00:08:31,198
We'll just see what's going on at first...

130
00:08:31,273 --> 00:08:34,071
If it looks too dangerous,
we won't battle for no reason.

131
00:08:34,143 --> 00:08:35,371
- Let's go!
- Oh!

132
00:08:36,479 --> 00:08:39,141
He's an irritating type, that one.

133
00:08:47,089 --> 00:08:49,057
What's up, Akamaru?

134
00:08:49,925 --> 00:08:52,189
What happened? You stopped suddenly.

135
00:08:55,164 --> 00:08:57,291
Akamaru suddenly got frightened.

136
00:08:57,766 --> 00:08:59,256
W-Why is that?

137
00:08:59,935 --> 00:09:04,338
Akamaru can sniff out the level of enemy's
Chakra and tell his strength.

138
00:09:04,974 --> 00:09:07,568
But this is the first time I've
seen him this scared.

139
00:09:08,677 --> 00:09:12,511
The people going at it up ahead
aren't ordinary guys...

140
00:09:17,286 --> 00:09:21,814
Sand Village kids coming
to challenge us forthright.

141
00:09:22,258 --> 00:09:23,691
It's foolish.

142
00:09:34,370 --> 00:09:39,034
What's that little guy thinking
to get involved with those guys?!

143
00:09:43,445 --> 00:09:45,037
W-What is Akamaru saying?

144
00:09:45,181 --> 00:09:48,480
He's saying that big guy is dangerous.

145
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:53,745
<i>T-They certainly look like bad news...</i>

146
00:09:54,223 --> 00:09:55,520
<i>They seem really strong.</i>

147
00:09:56,091 --> 00:09:59,754
Hey, kids, you should
pick your opponents...

148
00:10:00,462 --> 00:10:02,157
You're all going to die.

149
00:10:02,431 --> 00:10:03,955
That's enough of you.

150
00:10:04,533 --> 00:10:08,025
Let's do this quickly...
old chap from Hidden Rain Village.

151
00:10:09,605 --> 00:10:13,063
<i>Which scroll do those guys have...</i>

152
00:10:14,109 --> 00:10:14,939
Hey Gaara!

153
00:10:15,711 --> 00:10:17,303
Doesn't it make sense to
follow them

154
00:10:17,379 --> 00:10:19,540
and gather information
before hunting them?

155
00:10:20,082 --> 00:10:23,574
If they have the same type of scroll
there's no need to fight.

156
00:10:23,986 --> 00:10:25,010
Unnecessary battles are...

157
00:10:25,087 --> 00:10:26,349
It doesn't matter.

158
00:10:27,756 --> 00:10:31,214
If their eyes meet with mine...
I'll kill them all.

159
00:10:33,729 --> 00:10:37,495
<i>That's why I don't want</i>
<i>to be with this guy.</i>

160
00:10:39,101 --> 00:10:42,036
Well, let's do it. Quickly!

161
00:10:48,010 --> 00:10:49,068
Die, kid!

162
00:10:49,311 --> 00:10:51,506
Ninja Art: Senbon Rainstorm!

163
00:10:54,617 --> 00:10:55,709
<i>Hidden Senbons!</i>

164
00:11:02,358 --> 00:11:05,225
Up down right left,
there is no dead spot in this Jutsu.

165
00:11:05,594 --> 00:11:08,722
In addition, all the Senbons are
controlled by my Chakra

166
00:11:08,797 --> 00:11:10,822
and attack on the intended prey!

167
00:11:15,638 --> 00:11:16,696
<i>Too easy.</i>

168
00:11:25,114 --> 00:11:26,376
Is that all?

169
00:11:26,915 --> 00:11:28,007
I-It can't be?!

170
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:29,376
Not even one?

171
00:11:29,451 --> 00:11:32,113
No wounds? Ridiculous!

172
00:11:36,992 --> 00:11:38,721
Senbon Rainstorm, huh?

173
00:11:39,862 --> 00:11:43,662
Well, I'll make it rain blood.

174
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:54,954
What a giant Chakra.

175
00:11:55,528 --> 00:11:57,894
And, that sand...

176
00:11:58,832 --> 00:12:00,561
It smells terrible.

177
00:12:01,768 --> 00:12:02,792
Smell?

178
00:12:05,739 --> 00:12:07,730
A strong smell of blood...

179
00:12:09,809 --> 00:12:11,276
Wall of sand?

180
00:12:11,945 --> 00:12:15,813
That's right.
An absolute defense by sand!

181
00:12:16,683 --> 00:12:18,776
He manipulates sand inside
a gourd and

182
00:12:18,852 --> 00:12:20,683
hardens it with magnified Chakra.

183
00:12:21,121 --> 00:12:23,146
It defends the circumference
of Gaara's body.

184
00:12:23,223 --> 00:12:25,555
It's a Jutsu that only
he can get away with...

185
00:12:26,259 --> 00:12:28,659
Furthermore, it's somehow always
automatically done

186
00:12:28,728 --> 00:12:30,719
without Gaara's intentions.

187
00:12:31,765 --> 00:12:35,895
Which means that all attacks
in front of Gaara fade into nothing.

188
00:12:37,570 --> 00:12:38,537
That little...

189
00:12:38,838 --> 00:12:42,069
You guys can't defeat our Gaara.

190
00:12:42,976 --> 00:12:44,705
Don't underestimate me!

191
00:12:50,784 --> 00:12:52,376
<i>This guy's a goner...</i>

192
00:12:52,952 --> 00:12:54,977
<i>That's what you get for rebelling</i>
<i>against Gaara...</i>

193
00:12:56,423 --> 00:12:58,323
Sand Coffin!

194
00:13:08,568 --> 00:13:09,899
I can't move...

195
00:13:16,009 --> 00:13:18,068
T-This won't!

196
00:13:22,515 --> 00:13:26,144
I can cover your loud mouth
and kill you.

197
00:13:33,193 --> 00:13:35,388
But that's too pathetic.

198
00:14:00,854 --> 00:14:02,344
Sand Burial!

199
00:14:15,101 --> 00:14:16,864
There's no pain.

200
00:14:17,303 --> 00:14:20,761
I knocked him even harder
than was necessary.

201
00:14:21,408 --> 00:14:25,435
The bloody tears of a corpse merge
with vast sinking sand

202
00:14:25,912 --> 00:14:29,177
and provide more power
to the demon of war.

203
00:14:31,084 --> 00:14:32,574
T-The scroll.

204
00:14:32,952 --> 00:14:34,351
We'll give it to you!

205
00:14:35,955 --> 00:14:38,389
Please! Let us go!

206
00:14:44,964 --> 00:14:46,295
No-o-o-!

207
00:14:55,308 --> 00:14:56,468
T-This is bad.

208
00:14:56,776 --> 00:15:00,007
Let's escape quickly!
If he finds us he'll kill us!

209
00:15:04,384 --> 00:15:06,352
Luckily it is a Heaven scroll.

210
00:15:06,986 --> 00:15:09,420
Okay! Let's go to the tower.

211
00:15:09,656 --> 00:15:10,680
Shut up.

212
00:15:11,858 --> 00:15:14,691
It's still... not enough for me!

213
00:15:16,763 --> 00:15:19,630
<i>U-Uh oh! Did he notice us?!</i>

214
00:15:20,934 --> 00:15:22,925
Let's quit... Gaara.

215
00:15:25,238 --> 00:15:27,604
Are you scared, coward?

216
00:15:29,008 --> 00:15:35,072
Gaara! It's certainly no problem for you,
but it's too dangerous for us!

217
00:15:35,548 --> 00:15:37,539
One set of scrolls is good.

218
00:15:38,117 --> 00:15:39,448
More than this is...

219
00:15:41,821 --> 00:15:44,483
Lame people don't give directions to me.

220
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:48,988
That's enough!

221
00:15:49,596 --> 00:15:52,429
How about if you sometimes listen
to what your big brother has to say?!

222
00:15:53,266 --> 00:15:56,394
I've never thought of you as my siblings.

223
00:15:57,036 --> 00:15:59,937
If you get in my way... I'll kill you.

224
00:16:06,779 --> 00:16:09,577
G-Gaara cut it out! Please.

225
00:16:09,883 --> 00:16:12,215
Don't say something so cold.

226
00:16:12,652 --> 00:16:16,179
As a favor to your sister... Okay?!

227
00:16:39,646 --> 00:16:40,578
Gaara!

228
00:16:49,989 --> 00:16:51,513
Fine.

229
00:17:07,774 --> 00:17:09,867
<i>That's why I hate brats.</i>

230
00:17:17,350 --> 00:17:20,217
What? So that's it Akamaru?

231
00:17:20,653 --> 00:17:23,087
C'mon, you should have
said something sooner.

232
00:17:29,228 --> 00:17:30,388
Nobody's here?

233
00:17:31,297 --> 00:17:34,164
Heh heh! We're the first?!

234
00:17:34,500 --> 00:17:37,094
No, I sensed someone a little while ago.

235
00:17:38,204 --> 00:17:40,365
More importantly, is Akamaru okay?

236
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:43,206
He's been scared ever since then.

237
00:17:44,310 --> 00:17:47,177
Now that you mention it,
what did Akamaru say before?

238
00:17:47,614 --> 00:17:50,913
Oh... Akamaru said that it
was dangerous

239
00:17:50,984 --> 00:17:54,010
because that sand squirt
would kill that big guy.

240
00:17:54,587 --> 00:17:57,647
Sheesh! Just like I thought,
there's no other place to go!

241
00:17:58,424 --> 00:18:00,358
They've already made us
wait for half a day!

242
00:18:01,027 --> 00:18:02,619
How much longer do we have to wait?

243
00:18:20,980 --> 00:18:24,040
<i>Anyway. That Sand Village squirt...</i>

244
00:18:24,450 --> 00:18:27,578
<i>I don't know what he is but,</i>
<i>that guy...</i>

245
00:18:27,787 --> 00:18:29,186
<i>He's too dangerous.</i>

246
00:18:37,230 --> 00:18:41,792
It's becoming a real disaster,
but we can't cancel this test.

247
00:18:42,502 --> 00:18:43,799
What do you mean?

248
00:18:44,303 --> 00:18:45,133
Excuse me!

249
00:18:45,805 --> 00:18:48,740
What is it?!
We're talking about something important!

250
00:18:49,676 --> 00:18:50,472
Excuse me.

251
00:18:50,543 --> 00:18:51,567
But... Uh...

252
00:18:51,644 --> 00:18:52,633
Please take a look at this!

253
00:18:53,246 --> 00:18:54,338
The video?

254
00:18:58,718 --> 00:19:02,381
Ready? Here! Look at the time!

255
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:11,797
T-This is...

256
00:19:12,365 --> 00:19:13,957
It's a recording inside the tower,

257
00:19:14,033 --> 00:19:18,697
one hour and thirty seven minutes
after the start of the second test!

258
00:19:20,239 --> 00:19:24,141
<i>Three Ninja from Hidden Sand Village</i>
<i>broke through the second test.</i>

259
00:19:27,947 --> 00:19:29,312
This can't be!

260
00:19:29,649 --> 00:19:31,674
In a mere ninety seven minutes...

261
00:19:33,119 --> 00:19:35,019
This has never happened!

262
00:19:36,255 --> 00:19:37,586
This is an anomaly.

263
00:19:38,224 --> 00:19:40,283
Those guys are not Genin level.

264
00:19:40,927 --> 00:19:44,727
They've rewritten the
fastest time by four hours...

265
00:19:46,532 --> 00:19:47,863
It's not just that.

266
00:19:48,901 --> 00:19:50,232
What do you mean?

267
00:19:51,204 --> 00:19:54,662
It's 10 kilometers
from the test entrances to the tower.

268
00:19:55,007 --> 00:19:58,465
Ferocious animals, poisonous insects,
the rugged forest road...

269
00:19:58,945 --> 00:20:02,005
As if those were not there...

270
00:20:03,316 --> 00:20:05,511
Especially the brown haired kid
right in front...

271
00:20:06,586 --> 00:20:07,848
What about him?

272
00:20:08,254 --> 00:20:09,346
You don't notice?

273
00:20:15,361 --> 00:20:18,159
I see. This is quite a surprise.

274
00:20:19,198 --> 00:20:22,167
What about him is so?

275
00:20:22,902 --> 00:20:25,302
Look closely at his body.

276
00:20:35,114 --> 00:20:35,944
I see.

277
00:20:36,616 --> 00:20:38,311
He doesn't have a single scratch.

278
00:20:38,684 --> 00:20:42,745
What's worse, there's not
a smudge of dirt on his clothing.

279
00:20:43,556 --> 00:20:45,046
Even I...

280
00:20:45,224 --> 00:20:48,125
No, any of the other Chunin...

281
00:20:48,528 --> 00:20:51,691
It's impossible for us to
make it to this tower without a scratch.

282
00:20:52,365 --> 00:20:55,562
It's likely that it has something
to do with his ability.

283
00:20:56,335 --> 00:20:59,133
After a long time, a dependable
guy has appeared.

284
00:21:01,274 --> 00:21:02,832
Even though he's got evil eyes.

285
00:21:05,418 --> 00:21:10,151
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

286
00:21:10,256 --> 00:21:18,356
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

287
00:21:19,432 --> 00:21:27,965
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

288
00:21:28,574 --> 00:21:36,276
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

289
00:21:37,683 --> 00:21:43,212
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

290
00:21:43,289 --> 00:21:47,055
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

291
00:21:47,126 --> 00:21:50,687
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

292
00:21:51,163 --> 00:21:59,571
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

293
00:21:59,972 --> 00:22:05,035
<i>when you want to cry, and you want to run away</i>

294
00:22:05,111 --> 00:22:09,514
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

295
00:22:09,682 --> 00:22:13,345
<i>Just sing.</i>

296
00:22:13,653 --> 00:22:18,750
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

297
00:22:18,891 --> 00:22:21,018
<i>The two are one</i>

298
00:22:21,127 --> 00:22:27,396
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

299
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:32,994
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

300
00:22:37,743 --> 00:22:38,910
- Please!
- No!

301
00:22:38,910 --> 00:22:40,377
- Just a little bit.
- No!

302
00:22:40,445 --> 00:22:42,572
- Really only a little bit.
- No means no!

303
00:22:42,647 --> 00:22:45,138
I'll just look a little and put it back.

304
00:22:45,250 --> 00:22:47,741
Remember what the
Proctors said, loser.

305
00:22:48,120 --> 00:22:49,917
When they say don't look, don't look,

306
00:22:49,988 --> 00:22:52,047
it just makes me want
to look all the more!

307
00:22:52,190 --> 00:22:54,181
If you can look when you can,
let's look!

308
00:22:54,259 --> 00:22:55,089
Naruto lost it!

309
00:22:55,160 --> 00:22:56,559
Sakura! Get a hold of Naruto!

310
00:22:56,795 --> 00:23:00,094
Next episode: "The Scroll's Secret:
No Peeking Allowed

311
00:23:00,432 --> 00:23:02,127
I really want to look!
